==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: A newborn calf is not afraid of a tiger.
===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|s|pin=chū shēng zhī dú bù wèi hŭ|pint=chu1sheng1zhi1du2bu4wei4hu3|tra=初生之犢不畏虎|sim=初生之犊不畏虎|rs=刀05}}
# A young person is often willing to take risks.

